                are
                editable after generation.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
            <button class="faq-trigger" id="faq-q5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-a5">
              Can I use the plugin on multiple computers?
              <img src="assets/icons/plus.svg" class="faq-icon" alt="" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;">
