          </div>

          <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
            <button class="faq-trigger" id="faq-q6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-a6">
              What export formats are supported?
              <img src="assets/icons/plus.svg" class="faq-icon" alt="" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;">
            </button>
            <div class="faq-body" id="faq-a6" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-q6">
              <div class="faq-body-inner">
                It supports Adobe Premiere Pro native captions.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
            <button class="faq-trigger" id="faq-q7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-a7">
              What is your refund policy?
              <img src="assets/icons/plus.svg" class="faq-icon" alt="" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;">
            </button>
            <div class="faq-body" id="faq-a7" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-q7">
              <div class="faq-body-inner">
                We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee if Qwint Caption doesn't work as described. Contact our support
                team and we'll process your refund no questions asked. See our full <a href="/refund"
                  style="color:var(--clr-primary)">Refund Policy</a>.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item" role="listitem">
            <button class="faq-trigger" id="faq-q8" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-a8">
              Is my payment information secure?
              <img src="assets/icons/plus.svg" class="faq-icon" alt="" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;">
            </button>
            <div class="faq-body" id="faq-a8" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-q8">
              <div class="faq-body-inner">
                Yes. All payments are processed by Stripe a PCI DSS Level 1 certified payment processor. We never store
